{
  "stem": "5496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never lived in a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do very well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a beautiful corner apartment, with an entrance hall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then there was what they called the salon, which would be today's living room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then from my parent's bedroom, our bedroom, kitchen, bath, and a foyer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the address of my school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But funny, I don't remember that address, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ruzonberg was small, but it was a town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not a village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a town, and we walked to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Indeed, several of my friends were, and some were not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was, unfortunately, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certainly not more.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably the most would be 20%, I would assume.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were not Jewish, and we were very close friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that for Passover, we had the matzah, and that had to be brought in, I remember vividly, from somewhere else, because there were none available in Ruzonberg itself.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it must have been a small Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ones that were, we were rather assimilated, as the cliche goes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't in that stage of dating, so I wouldn't know anything about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I was much too young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we remained a very close-knit family, since my grandparents had only two children-- my mother and Aunt Rose.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very close, indeed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every Sunday, my grandfather with his chauffeur and a beautiful [? hotmobile ?] car would pick us up, and we would go in the nearby countryside or to a nearby resort.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There we would have all dinner on a lovely terrace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have recollections of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sports.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
